  <brief_title>Managing Severe Traumatic Brain Injury (TBI) Without Intracranial Pressure Monitoring (ICP) Monitoring Guidelines</brief_title>
  <official_title>Managing Severe Traumatic Brain Injury (TBI) Without Intracranial Pressure Monitoring (ICP)- Guidelines Development and Testing</official_title>
  <sponsors>
